           SHORT="Xorg video driver for DEC 21030 (aka TGA)"
cat << EOF
tga is an Xorg video driver for DEC 21030 (aka TGA).

The driver is partially accelerated. The built-in graphics on the
Multia is supported in 8-plane mode, and PCI cards with 8 or 16 MB
framebuffers are supported in 24-plane mode.

TGA2 (aka PowerStorm 3D30/4D20) cards are not currently supported.
EOF
